Gold_SQL_query: select t1.short_name, count(*) from node_table as t1 join edge_joinable_table_table as t2 on t1.node_id = t2.source_node_id group by t1.node_id, t1.short_name

NL_query: Order files by extension and from oldest to newest.
Gold_SQL_query: select short_name, extension, creation_date from node_file order by extension asc, creation_date asc

NL_query: How many nodes are present in the lake?
Gold_SQL_query: select count(*) from node

NL_query: Show the extension and size of the 25 most recently created files.
Gold_SQL_query: select extension, fsize, creation_date from node_file order by creation_date desc limit 25

NL_query: Display creation full name and description for the classification labeled 'state'.
Gold_SQL_query: select long_name, description from node_classification where short_name = 'state'

NL_query: Show all metadata for label association relationships created in the past week.
Gold_SQL_query: select * from edge_assoc where creation_date >= now() - interval '7 days'

NL_query: When was each business term created?
Gold_SQL_query: select short_name, creation_date from node_business_term

NL_query: Which are the relational databases in the lake owned by 'cslab'?
Gold_SQL_query: select t3.short_name from node_owner as t1 join edge_own as t2 on t1.node_id = t2.source_node_id join node_rdbms as t3 on t2.target_node_id = t3.node_id where t1.short_name = 'cslab'

NL_query: Count the number of columns for all tables created in the last one week.
Gold_SQL_query: select t1.node_id, t1.short_name, count(*) from node_table as t1 join edge_has_table_col as t2 on t1.node_id = t2.source_node_id where t1.creation_date >= now() - interval '7 days' group by t1.node_id, t1.short_name

NL_query: Count the number of different types of files in the lake?
Gold_SQL_query: select count(distinct extension) from node_file

NL_query: Show the database type and last modified date for all databases that were last modified in the past 30 days.
Gold_SQL_query: select database_type, modified_date from node_database where modified_date >= now() - interval '30 days'

NL_query: Find all tables in the lake that have 5 columns or more.
Gold_SQL_query: select short_name, num_cols from node_table where num_cols >= 5

NL_query: List all directory names with size greater than 1MB.
Gold_SQL_query: select short_name from node_directory where dsize > 1000

NL_query: Show the names of the last 5 modified directories.
Gold_SQL_query: select short_name, modified_date from node_directory order by modified_date desc

NL_query: Show all files with the extension and size in the lake.
Gold_SQL_query: select short_name, extension, fsize from node_file

NL_query: Show all tables that have 10 or more rows, 10 or more columns and were created in the last 10 days.
Gold_SQL_query: select short_name from node_table where num_rows >= 10 and num_cols >= 10 and creation_date >= now() - interval '10 days'

NL_query: List all tables that are unionable with the table 'swim_for_life'.
Gold_SQL_query: select t1.short_name from node_table as t1 join edge_unionable_table_table as t2 on t1.node_id = t2.target_node_id join node_table as t3 on t2.source_node_id = t3.node_id where t3.short_name = 'swim_for_life'

NL_query: Count owner accounts.
Gold_SQL_query: select count(*) from node_owner

NL_query: What are the folders present in the lake?
Gold_SQL_query: select short_name from node_directory

NL_query: For each table, count the number of columns associated with the classification 'customer'.
Gold_SQL_query: select t1.node_id, t1.short_name, count(*) from node_table as t1 join edge_has_table_col as t2 on t1.node_id = t2.source_node_id join edge_assoc_class_col as t3 on t2.target_node_id = t3.target_node_id join node_classification as t4 on t3.source_node_id = t4.node_id where t4.short_name = 'customer' group by t1.node_id, t1.short_name

NL_query: Print the creation date, description and last modification date for the sales database.
Gold_SQL_query: select creation_date, description, modified_date from node_database where short_name = 'sales_db'

NL_query: How many columns does each asset owner own?
Gold_SQL_query: select t1.short_name, count(*) from node_owner as t1 join edge_own as t2 on t1.node_id = t2.source_node_id join node_column as t3 on t2.target_node_id = t3.node_id group by t1.node_id, t1.short_name

NL_query: List all assets owned by 'cslab'.
Gold_SQL_query: select t3.short_name from node_owner as t1 join edge_own as t2 on t1.node_id = t2.source_node_id join node as t3 on t2.target_node_id = t3.node_id where t1.short_name = 'cslab'

NL_query: Show the type ids and counts for each asset type that contains more than 25 instances.
Gold_SQL_query: select type_id, count(*) from node group by type_id having count(*) > 25

NL_query: Print all records created in the past 3 days for relations outlining a column within a table.
Gold_SQL_query: select * from edge_has_table_col where creation_date >= now() - interval '3 days'

NL_query: Order the csv files in the data lake from the most recently created to the least recently created.
Gold_SQL_query: select short_name from node_file where extension = 'csv' order by creation_date desc

NL_query: Display the column type, column length and description for each column with length greater than 100 characters.
Gold_SQL_query: select short_name, col_type, max_col_length, description from node_column where max_col_length > 100

NL_query: Show the name, long name and description for all folders that contain at least one file directly inside them.
Gold_SQL_query: select t1.short_name, t1.long_name, t1.description from node_directory as t1 join edge_has_dir_file as t2 on t1.node_id = t2.source_node_id

NL_query: Which tables were obtained from files with the prefix 'watershed_water_quality'?
Gold_SQL_query: select t3.short_name from node_file as t1 join edge_has_file_table as t2 on t1.node_id = t2.source_node_id join node_table as t3 on t2.target_node_id = t3.node_id where t1.short_name like 'watershed_water_quality%'

NL_query: Print short name, long name and description for files in the HR directory.
Gold_SQL_query: select t3.short_name, t3.long_name, t3.description from node_directory as t1 join edge_has_dir_file as t2 on t1.node_id = t2.source_node_id join node_file as t3 on t2.target_node_id = t3.node_id where t3.short_name = 'human_resources'

NL_query: Show the total size of all files added in the last 30 days for each owner account.
Gold_SQL_query: select t1.node_id, t1.short_name, sum(t3.fsize) from node_owner as t1 join edge_own as t2 on t1.node_id = t2.source_node_id join node_file as t3 on t2.target_node_id = t3.node_id where t3.creation_date >= now() - interval '30 days' group by t1.node_id, t1.short_name

NL_query: Show all metadata records for all classification label column association relations.
Gold_SQL_query: select * from edge_assoc_class_col

NL_query: Print the creation dates and descriptions of all business terms in the lake.
Gold_SQL_query: select short_name, creation_date, description from node_business_term

NL_query: Which are the columns that are associated with the classification 'enterprise'?
Gold_SQL_query: select t3.short_name from node_classification as t1 join edge_assoc_class_col as t2 on t1.node_id = t2.source_node_id join node_column as t3 on t2.target_node_id = t3.node_id where t1.short_name = 'enterprise'

NL_query: What are the 25 oldest folders in the data lake?
Gold_SQL_query: select short_name, creation_date from node_directory order by creation_date asc limit 25

NL_query: Find all assets with the term 'prod' in it's name or description.
Gold_SQL_query: select short_name, description from node where short_name like '%prod%' or description like '%prod%'

NL_query: Locate records for all columns named 'std_cost'.
Gold_SQL_query: select * from node_column where short_name = 'std_cost'

NL_query: How many total relations are represented in the data lake?
Gold_SQL_query: select count(*) from edge

NL_query: What are the files and folders directly under folder 'sales'?
Gold_SQL_query: select t3.short_name from node_directory as t1 join edge_has as t2 on t1.node_id = t2.source_node_id join node as t3 on t2.target_node_id = t3.node_id where t1.short_name = 'sales'

NL_query: List all records for the csv file named 'prospective_buyer'.
Gold_SQL_query: select * from node_file where short_name = 'prospective_buyer' and extension = 'csv'

NL_query: Which assets have the word 'scenario' in their name or description?
Gold_SQL_query: select short_name, description from node where short_name like '%scenario%' or description like '%scenario%'

NL_query: List the top 10 people who own the most relational databases.
Gold_SQL_query: select t1.short_name from node_owner as t1 join edge_own as t2 on t1.node_id = t2.source_node_id join node_rdbms as t3 on t2.target_node_id = t3.node_id group by t1.node_id, t1.short_name order by count(*) limit 10

NL_query: Count the number of nodes in the graph for the lake.
Gold_SQL_query: select count(*) from node

NL_query: Print all metadata for joinable table relationships created in the past 3 days.
Gold_SQL_query: select * from edge_joinable_table_table where creation_date >= now() - interval '3 days'

NL_query: Sort databases in the lake by their last modified timestamp.
Gold_SQL_query: select short_name from node_database order by modified_date desc

NL_query: Show the number of assets owned by all accounts that have been modified in the past 1 day. The owner name must be detailed.
Gold_SQL_query: select t1.long_name, count(*) from node_owner as t1 join edge_own as t2 on t1.node_id = t2.source_node_id where t1.modified_date >= now() - interval '24 hours' group by t1.node_id, t1.long_name
